{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f1bd79ed9c","title":"致华东、中原两野战军首长等电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e4b8265ede","index":0,"year":1949,"month":1,"day":17,"articleId":"f1bd79ed9c"}],"tags":[{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji25","name":"毛泽东全集第25卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji25.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji25":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9ac9009e92","type":"paragraph","text":"致华东、中原两野战军首长等电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"f1bd79ed9c"},{"id":"d05d7b00b4","type":"paragraph","text":"（1949年1月17日）准海战役既然消灭了南线国民党军的主力，这就英定了你们测江南进夺取国民党亚集南京，并解放江南各省的巩固的基础[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央起草的致华东、中原两野战军首长和全体同给宋庆龄的两封信","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"f1bd79ed9c"},{"id":"c4229764ca","type":"paragraph","text":"（1949年1月19日、6月19日）庆龄先生中国革命胜利的形势已使反动派临死亡的末日，沪上环境如何，至所系念。新的政治协商会议将在华北召开，中国人民革命历尽限辛，中山先生遗志运今始告实现，至析先生命驾北来，参加此一人民历史伟大的事业，并对于如何建设新中国予以指导。至于如何由沪北上，已告梦醒与汉年、仲华切商，总期以安全为第一通电致意，仁盼回音。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"f1bd79ed9c"},{"id":"6e8f126118","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东周恩来","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"f1bd79ed9c"},{"id":"0f7a6ae950","type":"paragraph","text":"子皓周恩来秘书。[I]梦醒，即廖梦醒（1904-1988），广东离阳人，当时是宋庆龄的12]汉年，即滑汉年，当时是中国共产党派往上海、香港开展统一战线工作的负责人。件华，即金传华（1907-1968），浙江桐乡人，当时在上海庆龄先生重庆违教，忽近四年。仰望之诚，与日俱积。兹者全国革命胜利在即，建设大计，或待商筹，特派邓颗超同志趋前致候，专诚欢迎先生北上。敬希命驾莅平，以便就近请教，至祈勿却为盼！专此。敬颂大安！","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"f1bd79ed9c"},{"id":"46ab798737","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"f1bd79ed9c"},{"id":"f469d8d582","type":"paragraph","text":"一九四九年六月十九日i]邓颖超，当时任中共中央候补委员、中华全国民主妇女联合会融","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"f1bd79ed9c"},{"id":"366f1e1a80","type":"paragraph","text":"","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"f1bd79ed9c"},{"id":"f389a414c6","type":"paragraph","text":"中国共萨7/您0","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"f1bd79ed9c"},{"id":"f18aa586f4","type":"paragraph","text":"容","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"f1bd79ed9c"},{"id":"34a382bf0b","type":"paragraph","text":"复","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"f1bd79ed9c"},{"id":"8d3d637650","type":"paragraph","text":"中","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"f1bd79ed9c"},{"id":"a2f22b7362","type":"paragraph","text":"中2毛泽东邀请宋庆龄北上的亲笔信（信封）","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"f1bd79ed9c"},{"id":"bb0e7951c3","type":"paragraph","text":"公","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"f1bd79ed9c"},{"id":"3a30eb5841","type":"paragraph","text":"为复③州州神润安用兴然大计复③","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"f1bd79ed9c"},{"id":"c9a76b90a2","type":"paragraph","text":"机包运号","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"f1bd79ed9c"},{"id":"a756b8f634","type":"paragraph","text":"中2","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"f1bd79ed9c"},{"id":"7ac2adc997","type":"paragraph","text":"汉店变央中费帝共","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"f1bd79ed9c"},{"id":"8dba4ad870","type":"paragraph","text":"前新滨事开城藏逸五","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"f1bd79ed9c"},{"id":"f57f8306ed","type":"paragraph","text":"二希布迎放子哈","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"f1bd79ed9c"}],"page":{"id":"ccf6f14832","publicationId":"maoquanji25","articleId":"f1bd79ed9c","start":540,"end":544}}}},"__N_SSG":true}